data.description: Spacious 5 bedroom, 3 bath home in PHM School District located on a private cul de sac.  The master suite features walk in shower and his/her walk in closets.  The large kitchen has granite countertops and large island, hand scraped plank flooring.  The laundry room is located on the second floor.  Finished basement area that includes Everdry waterproofing system.  The large fenced yard includes a stocked pond, apple and pear trees and for the gun enthusiast a gun range certified by the St. Joe County Sheriff  Department, also has an oversized attached two car garage.  Located close to Baugo Park. Seller will consider giving buyer allowance for carpet and paint with an acceptable offer.     Welcome Home!
